{"tid":1614303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺講唔好俾仇恨上腦，自己變成藍絲黑警好似d人做gym怕做得太大隻？","createTime":"2019-10-02T17:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T09:47:31.000Z","uid":25617,"like":61,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c5aa63d7d71ab806e85801a212809629d1c5ecd3","tid":1614303,"uid":25617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:47:04.000Z","msg":"屌你人唔笑狗都吠<br />\n爆藍鋪又無偷野又無搞到客人，有原則道理去做既事，你拎黎同藍絲黑警比？<br />\n咩叫對唔準政權？呢d藍店為政權說項賣命，indigo篤灰，中資送錢俾中共維穩<br />\n好啦要對準政權，想問你點對準？四個月黎夠準未？幾多個手足俾人拉左？<br />\n宜家be water快閃做其他野你又唔滿意，其實你想點撚樣<br />\n另外一單，廢老拎刀斬手足俾人私了班阻膠話同黑警有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n根本你班廢柴阻膠就係意志唔堅定左搖右擺，成撚日念茲在茲就係個民意<br />\n宜家黑警一槍打撚死手足呀想屌你老母民意<br />\n跟手語氣極差一副教人做野咁款<br />\n其實真係好撚柒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a4621ecdad03e5fe09d9a65267aa0b9dcea582","tid":1614303,"uid":25617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:54:40.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e1364b8d4b808185a41f87288dd3b7b753679d","tid":1614303,"uid":25617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:55:40.000Z","msg":"唔洗你地教人做野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c78aab75b84358706145f0c3176a11454cde128","tid":1614303,"uid":25617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb03558f753626d0bdcea4417d20d68dfacf4f89","tid":1614303,"uid":25617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18220c2574df6511104bfa233